According to Global Citizen, since 2011, they have recorded 19 million “acts” of their supporters aimed at achieving various goals.
The organization claims that these actions prompted world leaders to announce planned financial allocations and programs worth more than $ 37 billion, which by 2030 will help change the lives of more than 2.25 billion people.
